export function Aside({ chosenAnime }) { const producers = chosenAnime?.producers ?.map((el) => el) .map((el) => el.name) .join(" , "); const licensors = chosenAnime?.licensors ?.map((el) => el) .map((el) => el.name) .join(" , "); return (
Title: {chosen[0]?.title}
Type: {chosen[0]?.type}
Episodes: {chosen[0]?.episodes}
Status: {chosen[0]?.status}
Aired: {chosen[0]?.aired?.string}
{/*
Premiered: {chosen[0]?.pr}
*/}
Producers: {producers}
Licensors:{licensors}
Studios: {chosen[0]?.studios[0]?.name}
Source: {chosen[0]?.source}
Theme: {chosen[0]?.themes[0]?.name}
Demographic: {chosen[0]?.demographics[0]?.name}
Duration: {chosen[0]?.duration}
Rating: {chosen[0]?.rating}
); }
